European Stocks Gain; Benchmark Stoxx 600 Rebounds From Three-Month Low

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-06-27T07:31:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/european-stocks-gain-benchmark-stoxx-600-rebounds-from-three-month-low.html
European stocks advanced, rebounding
from a three-month low for the benchmark Stoxx Europe 600 Index,
as automakers and household-goods companies climbed.  The Stoxx 600 gained 0.3 percent to 264.82 at 8:30 a.m. in
 London , having earlier lost 0.3 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  